  <h1 class="case-study__title">1,115 people told us what's wrong with their watch list</h1>
  <p class="case-study__intro">
    "Mijn Lijst" is one of the most visited pages on VRT MAX — but it was stuck in a simple
    chronological view with no way to sort, filter, or organize. I ran a deep-dive user survey
    to understand how people actually use their list, why some don't, and what would make it better.
    1,115 responses later, the findings reshaped the feature's roadmap.
  </p>

  <div class="case-study__stats">
    <div class="case-study__stat">
      <div class="case-study__stat-number">1,115</div>
      <div class="case-study__stat-label">Survey responses</div>
    </div>
